---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - BatesAI" description="Learn about BatesAI">
  <div class="min-h-screen pt-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-bold mb-4">
          About <span class="text-bates-cyan">BatesAI</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">Built by an independent developer</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-cyan max-w-none">
        <div class="p-10 rounded-2xl bg-bates-navy/30 border border-bates-cyan/20 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-bates-cyan">The Story</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            BatesAI is a solo developer project focused on building practical tools that solve everyday problems.
            No team, no funding, just one person experimenting with AI and automation to create useful software.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Every project here started as a personal need: managing battery life on macOS, tracking photography gear prices,
            or summarizing endless emails. If it helps me, maybe it'll help you too.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-bates-cyan/10 to-bates-navy/30 border border-bates-cyan/20">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸŽ¯</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-bates-cyan">The Approach</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Build simple tools that solve specific problems. No bloat, no unnecessary features.
              If it doesn't work for me first, it doesn't ship.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-bates-cyan/10 to-bates-navy/30 border border-bates-cyan/20">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ðŸ’¡</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-bates-cyan">Open Development</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300">
              Most projects are open source on GitHub. Feel free to contribute, fork, or just see how things work.
              Transparency over marketing.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="p-10 rounded-2xl bg-bates-navy/30 border border-bates-cyan/20 mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-bates-cyan">Current Focus</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300 text-lg">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-bates-cyan text-2xl">âœ“</span>
              <span>Chrome extensions for email management and price tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-bates-cyan text-2xl">âœ“</span>
              <span>macOS utilities for battery management and automation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-bates-cyan text-2xl">âœ“</span>
              <span>Python automation scripts for photo management and workflow</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-bates-cyan text-2xl">âœ“</span>
              <span>Experimenting with AI integration in everyday tools</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-bates-cyan/20 to-bates-navy/50 border border-bates-cyan/30">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Want to Connect?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Have an idea, found a bug, or just want to chat? Reach out.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-bates-cyan text-bates-dark rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:glow-cyan-strong transition">
              Get in Touch
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/danielalanbates" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 border-2 border-bates-cyan text-bates-cyan rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-bates-cyan/10 transition">
              View on GitHub
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
